and then convert RSA key from DER to PEM format using function from [here][1] before setting it up in crypt.setPublicKey():

````
&lt;?php
function der2pem($der_data, $type=&#39;CERTIFICATE&#39;) {
   $pem = chunk_split(base64_encode($der_data), 64, &quot;\n&quot;);
   $pem = &quot;-----BEGIN &quot;.$type.&quot;-----\n&quot;.$pem.&quot;-----END &quot;.$type.&quot;-----\n&quot;;
   return $pem;
}

?&gt;
````
